# ⚡ Getting Started

### 1️⃣ Clone repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/taskio.git
```

---

### 2️⃣ Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

---

### 3️⃣ Run development server

```bash
npm run dev
```

Then open:

```
http://localhost:3000
```

